    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the salmon is cooking, chop your <strong>cucumber</strong> roughly</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped cucumber</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong></p>",
