    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> spinach</strong>, then add to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over it so that it starts to wilt</p><p>Rinse the <strong>wilted spinach</strong> under the <strong>cold running water</strong> until it's cool</p><p>Squeeze out any excess water and add the <strong>wilted spinach</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your<strong> sesame spinach</strong></p>",
