      "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> mayo</strong> with your<strong> sriracha</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a small bowl – this is your <strong>sriracha mayo</strong></p><p>Flake the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>salmon</strong> into bite-sized pieces with a fork</p>",
