    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> flaked salmon</strong>, <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong>, <strong>sesame spinach </strong>on top of the <strong>cooked brown rice</strong> and drizzle over the <strong>sriracha mayo</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> sliced spring onion</strong>, <strong>black sesame seeds </strong>and<strong> sliced red chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
